 begin="30.200" end="30.300">ror</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">因为你闪耀得宛如一面明镜</span></p><p begin="30.390" end="32.060" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="30.390" end="30.490">And</span> <span begin="30.490" end="30.610">I</span> <span begin="30.610" end="30.780">can</span><span begin="30.780" end="30.810">&apos;t</span> <span begin="30.810" end="31.010">help</span> <span begin="31.010" end="31.080">but</span> <span begin="31.180" end="31.780">no</span><span begin="31.780" end="32.000">ti</span><span begin="32.000" end="32.060">ce</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不禁注意到</span></p><p begin="32.340" end="35.780" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="32.340" end="32.560">You</span> <span begin="32.560" end="32.720">re</span><span begin="32.720" end="32.780">f</span><span begin="32.780" end="33.180">lec</span><span begin="33.330" end="33.520">ting</span> <span begin="33.520" end="33.640">thi</span><span begin="33.640" end="33.730">s</span> <span begin="33.730" end="33.910">hear</span><span begin="33.910" end="33.950">t</span> <span begin="33.950" end="33.990">of</span> <span begin="34.140" end="35.780">mine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你映照出了我的心</span></p><p begin="37.020" end="42.640" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="37.020" end="37.170">I</span><span begin="37.170" end="37.230">f</span> <span begin="37.230" end="37.430">you</span> <span begin="37.430" end="37.990">e</span><span begin="37.990" end="38.580">ver</span> <span begin="38.580" end="38.800">feel</span> <span begin="38.800" end="38.990">a</span><span begin="38.990" end="39.590">lone</span> <span begin="39.590" end="39.930">and</span> <span begin="40.360" end="40.420">the</span> <span begin="40.530" end="40.580">g</span><span begin="40.580" end="41.100">lare</span> <span begin="41.100" end="41.220">ma</span><span begin="41.220" end="41.320">kes</span> <span begin="41.320" end="41.510">me</span> <span begin="41.510" end="